dct_description_sm: tracé par le Sr. Pierre De Val Secretaire de Monseignr. l'Evesque.
Key in upper right: Marques de ceste carte.
Decorative cartouches with figures and cherubs, compass rose, latitudinal and longitudinal lines, ships.
Latin in key and cardinal directions.
